# ClimaTales AR — Android APK Next Steps

## Prerequisites
- [ ] Install Android Studio from https://developer.android.com/studio
  - During install, check "Android SDK", "Android SDK Platform", "Android Virtual Device"
  - Open Android Studio once after install to complete SDK setup and accept licenses
  - Ensure ANDROID_HOME is set (typically C:\Users\dmfaj\AppData\Local\Android\Sdk)

## Build the APK
- [ ] Run: cd android && ./gradlew assembleDebug
  - Output: android/app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk

## Test on Device/Emulator
- [ ] Install on device: adb install android/app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk
- [ ] Verify home page loads
- [ ] Navigate to /videos — local videos play, YouTube links open in system browser
- [ ] Navigate to /ar — camera permission prompt appears, AR tracking works
- [ ] Navigate to /quiz/2 — quiz loads, answers persist in localStorage

## Future: Play Store Distribution
- [ ] Move videos/models to a CDN or use Play Asset Delivery (APK currently ~292MB, Play Store limit is 150MB)
- [ ] Generate signed release AAB: ./gradlew bundleRelease
- [ ] Set up signing key and upload to Google Play Console
